{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"c03ce4e3-5c64-4a00-bbe1-ee5ad5b922bf","content":"There's no workflow file in the current directory, so here's general guidance for the switch:\n\n### Changes needed for NuGet Trusted Publishing (OIDC)\n\n**1. On nuget.org** — configure a Trusted Publisher:\n- Go to your package → Manage → Publishing → Add Trusted Publisher\n- Set your GitHub repo owner, repo name, workflow filename, and optionally the environment name\n\n**2. In your workflow** — three key changes:\n\n```yaml\n# ① Add id-token permission\npermissions:\n  id-token: write   # required for OIDC\n  contents: read\n\n# ② Replace your push step:\n# BEFORE:\n- run: dotnet nuget push **/*.nupkg --api-key ${{ secrets.NUGET_API_KEY }} --source https://api.nuget.org/v3/index.json\n\n# AFTER:\n- run: dotnet nuget push **/*.nupkg --source https://api.nuget.org/v3/index.json\n```\n\n**3. Remove** the `NUGET_API_KEY` secret from your repo settings once verified.\n\n### Key points\n- **No API key needed** — the `dotnet nuget push` command automatically uses the OIDC token when `id-token: write` is set and trusted publishing is configured on nuget.org.\n- If you use a **GitHub environment** (e.g., `production`), specify it in both the workflow job and the nuget.org trusted publisher config for tighter scoping.\n- You may also need `--api-key az` as a placeholder on older SDK versions (the value is ignored but the flag may be required).\n\nWould you like me to create a sample workflow file?","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"b7484af2-031d-46fe-a38c-8814967e1d5f","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The directory is empty - there's no existing workflow file to look at. The user is asking a general question about switching from NuGet API key authentication to NuGet trusted publishing (OIDC) in GitHub Actions. Let me provide guidance based on my knowledge.","outputTokens":467,"requestId":"C005:307F5D:8154843:8F84142:69EABE91"},"id":"1f75963e-4e8c-45eb-bda2-740f580075fe","timestamp":"2026-04-24T00:51:41.766Z","parentId":"f57d5abe-dda8-4323-9c55-451de1dc02b3"}
